description:
On March 9, Ansem posted a public fundraiser to put dogwifhat on the Las Vegas Sphere (see https://twitter.com/blknoiz06/status/1766680047547494658).

This market will resolve to "Yes" if the full $650,000 USDC (or equivalent) is raised for WIF sphere according to the on-chain fundraiser address (https://solscan.io/account/GLgvFH6Gn6uhXS8gJoZaykJ3uSP65FMoyC9aEveHF8Nn) by Friday, March 15, 2024, 11:59 PM ET. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

Changes in the fundraising address will be considered as long as the full $650,000 USDC (or equivalent) is raised by Friday,

The resolution source for this market will be the WIF sphere website (https://wif-sphere.vercel.app/) and on-chain sources, however a consensus of credible reporting will also be used.
